            "body": "Ah, my assumption was that `findfunc` semantically still represents \"find file-like targets\", even if the completion backend is custom. But I can also see the argument that once `findfunc` is set, Neovim can no longer guarantee the returned items are actual filesystem paths. \n\nThanks for the clarification.",
